* HybridPDR by Flask

To build javascript:
$ npm install
To hot-reload javascript:
$ npm run start
cf. https://github.com/jwkvam/minimal-flask-react

For example:
$ virtualenv --system-site-packages -p python3 .
$ source ./bin/activate
(venv) $ pip3 install --upgrade flask

To run app with hot-reload:
(venv) $ export FLASK_APP=./flask.py
(venv) $ export FLASK_DEBUG=1
(venv) $ export FLASK_ENV=development
(venv) $ flask run
